Name: Average time for Queued + Awaiting Assignment across all process variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Queued + Awaiting Assignment before transitioning to Accepted + In Progress
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Minimum time for Queued + Awaiting Assignment when followed by Accepted + Wait - User
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Average duration of Queued + Awaiting Assignment in variants that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Average time between Queued + Awaiting Assignment and Completed + In Call, considering only variants containing both
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Minimum time for Queued + Awaiting Assignment in variants that do not contain Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Average time for Queued + Awaiting Assignment when it appears multiple times in the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Total time from case start until Queued + Awaiting Assignment is first performed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Average time from Queued + Awaiting Assignment to Completed + Resolved in variants ending with Completed + Closed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time between consecutive occurrences of Queued + Awaiting Assignment within the same case
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Average duration of Queued + Awaiting Assignment in variants where Completed + In Call occurs after the last Queued + Awaiting Assignment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Total time spent in Queued + Awaiting Assignment in variants that transition directly to Accepted + In Progress without intermediate waits
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average time from Queued + Awaiting Assignment to Accepted + Assigned when both appear consecutively
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Minimum time for Queued + Awaiting Assignment in high-frequency variants (frequency > 100) that also include Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case
